{"tid":2495230,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"歐菲光被Apple踢出供應鏈後，總營收減少 6.97%，利潤減少 462.88%！大虧 80 億！","createTime":"2021-04-19T05:18:09.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-19T13:10:24.000Z","uid":109923,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2ff10efa37b8424ae25a32ef8aa43047b80889f9","tid":2495230,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T05:18:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://technews.tw/2021/04/19/apple-ofilm/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftechnews.tw%2F2021%2F04%2F19%2Fapple-ofilm%2F&d=CDYmK9DOGPUFxvwNhHfqxwQPoALeJAOsJ3HVvkpnkS8%3D&h=14a30662\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://technews.tw/2021/04/19/apple-ofilm/</a><br />\n<br />\n經過修正之後，歐菲光 2020 年的總營收為人民幣 483.5 億元，年減 6.97%；而在淨利潤方面則虧損 18.5 億人民幣，較 2019 年同期大幅滑落 462.88%。歐菲光在之前發布的業績快報中，預測 2020 年營收為 484 億元，年減 6.87%，但營業淨利潤為 8.1 至 9.1 億人民幣；在經過修正後，已由盈轉虧。"},{"pid":"edd3daad0451bf508f246116938195f867028e3c","tid":2495230,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T05:18:52.000Z","msg":"一冇中共補貼利潤就減咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2086f01228558cd7c99ae5a50d2eefb937040c89","tid":2495230,"uid":311701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T05:52:26.000Z","msg":"勾結外國勢力？"},{"pid":"be224577e0a9b1b21f877b2df8116f27b96ced08","tid":2495230,"uid":41818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T09:16:08.000Z","msg":"cls<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"597a5460aa5d8c3eaeb795f73a6204d1ce875338","tid":2495230,"uid":226155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T10:21:53.000Z","msg":"一直都話用各項壓力逼Apple 供應鏈去中國化好過"},{"pid":"bf53e7ecd1471ac0f5c05f556d0f86af5c13b984","tid":2495230,"uid":59511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"597a5460aa5d8c3eaeb795f73a6204d1ce875338","tid":2495230,"uid":226155,"like":0,"dislike"